spec_data.Name: texlive-mathalfa
spec_data.Description:
The package provides means of loading maths alphabets (such as
are normally addressed via macros \mathcal, \mathbb, \mathfrak
and \mathscr), offering various features normally missing in
existing packages for this job.
spec_data.Signature: RSA/SHA256, Sun 06 Aug 2017 08:28:42 AM EDT, Key ID f55e7430f5282ee4
spec_data.Summary: General package for loading maths alphabets in LaTeX
